	<article id="post-3274" class="post-3274 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-democracy category-intelligence category-law category-manning category-politics category-spies category-tv category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-35-years tag-bradley-manning tag-chelsea-manning tag-intelligence-2 tag-law-2 tag-politics-2 tag-prison tag-rt tag-war tag-whistleblowers-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/08/rt-interview-manning-sentencing.html" title="Permalink to RT interview on Manning sentencing" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> interview on Manning sentencing</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/08/rt-interview-manning-sentencing.html" title="14:31" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-08-25T14:31:22+00:00" pubdate>August 25, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
