                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is my most recent <span class="caps">RT</span> inter­view, live as Chelsea Man­ning was sen­tenced to 35 years in a <span class="caps">US</span> prison for blow­ing the whistle and expos­ing war crimes:<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/73015460" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
