				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/assange" rel="tag">Assange</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/extradition-2" rel="tag">extradition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/internment" rel="tag">internment</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/machon" rel="tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/manning" rel="tag">Manning</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/politics-2" rel="tag">politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/qatada" rel="tag">Qatada</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rights" rel="tag">rights</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/terrorism-2" rel="tag">terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
