				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/911" rel="tag">9/11</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/canada-tour-2009" rel="tag">Canada tour 2009</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/politics-2" rel="tag">politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/terrorism-2" rel="tag">terrorism</a>			</span>
						
