	<article id="post-187" class="post-187 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-civil-liberties category-democracy category-intelligence category-law category-machon category-mi5 category-mi6 category-national-security category-politics category-spies category-talks-2 category-whistleblowers tag-annie-machon tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-eth-o tag-intelligence-2 tag-politics-2 tag-spies-2 tag-talk tag-whistleblowing">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2009/05/eth0-talk-january-2009.html" title="Permalink to ETH0 Hacker Camp, January 2009" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">ETH0</span> Hacker Camp, January 2009</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2009/05/eth0-talk-january-2009.html" title="16:28" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2009-05-04T16:28:14+00:00" pubdate>May 4, 2009</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2009/05/eth0-talk-january-2009.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>In Janu­ary 2009 I was invited to talk at <a href="http://www.google.de/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;ct=res&amp;cd=1&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eth-0.nl%2F&amp;ei=dAz_SarQOsndsgby0fnOCQ&amp;usg=AFQjCNFdR8Exb9dQeC5pe1_UoNkSooqsLw&amp;sig2=9LOssiV3uaBYp5KzLvVZjQ"><span class="caps">ETH0</span></a>, a small but select hacker camp held in the wilds of the Neth­er­lands.  The crowd was young, hip, informed — and very inter­ested in the use and abuse of intel­li­gence and par­tic­u­larly the erosion of our most basic civil liber­ties.   Events like this give me hope.</p>
<p>Some of the organ­isers are also involved in plan­ning a major techno-political hacker fest­ival, <a href="http://www.google.de/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;ct=res&amp;cd=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fhar2009.org%2F&amp;ei=8wz_SaiYJoPE_Qavg_XLBA&amp;usg=AFQjCNE99PqLD7xOLXsrvtefm5ZqKoxS_w&amp;sig2=6SZcvDA5OXbeFxk3we5hbg">Hack­ing at Ran­dom</a>, in <span class="caps">NL</span> this sum­mer.   An event not to be missed!</p>
<p><a href="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=-6332661900693343330&amp;hl=nl" style="left: 0px ! important; top: 0px ! important;"></a></p>
<p><embed id="VideoPlayback" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=5267864304336545731&amp;hl=nl" style="width: 500px; height: 410px;">
<p><a title="Block this object with Adblock Plus" class="utbmjcutmptzrvdplofk" href="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=5267864304336545731&amp;hl=nl"></a></p>
<p><a style="left: 500px ! important; top: -3.51666px ! important;" title="Block this object with Adblock Plus" class="utbmjcutmptzrvdplofk visible" href="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=3107386605038300156&amp;hl=nl"></a></p>
</p>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
