				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/civil-liberties-2" rel="tag">civil liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/eth-o" rel="tag">ETH-O</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/politics-2" rel="tag">politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/talk" rel="tag">talk</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowing" rel="tag">whistleblowing</a>			</span>
						
