				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/accountability-2" rel="tag">accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/democracy-2" rel="tag">democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gchq" rel="tag">GCHQ</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/isa" rel="tag">ISA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/isc" rel="tag">ISC</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi6" rel="tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/osa" rel="tag">OSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/oversight" rel="tag">oversight</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/politics-2" rel="tag">politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ssa" rel="tag">SSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
